{"tid":2223860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方重新拘捕4人 涉嫌8.5 天水圍警署外非法集結","createTime":"2020-09-30T06:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T07:31:15.000Z","uid":44209,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b85ecc5c1f96fb528634a1f56b41615860fc9aae","tid":2223860,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"【 踢保不等於終止調查 &bull; 四人再被捕 &bull; 已落案控告 】<br />\n<br />\n去年‪8月5日，大批暴徒在天水圍警署外一帶非法集結。警方於當晚拘捕多人，部分被捕人及後拒絕保釋（俗稱「踢保」）。<br />\n<br />\n警方經深入調查及詢律政司意見後，於今日（9月30日）以「非法集結」及「抗拒執行職責的警務人員」等罪名重新拘捕並落案控告涉案的兩男兩女（年齡介乎19至24歲）。他們將於‪10月16日在屯門裁判法院提堂。‬"},{"pid":"ce38d61ca0e4b7b5c916c4248f2f43059fd73459","tid":2223860,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a5831918e71510b1bba165ff557ef2e2d1e1f8","tid":2223860,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"抗暴之戰｜4男女去年8.5罷工集會被捕踢保 今日再遭警方拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200930/GQSY75H5ZJESPMEI2V3GQWT34A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200930%2FGQSY75H5ZJESPMEI2V3GQWT34A%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=167675cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200930%2FGQSY75H5ZJESPMEI2V3GQWT34A%2F&h=d6c3a385\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200930/GQSY75H5ZJESPMEI2V3GQWT34A/</a>"},{"pid":"564b856e9d188d09aa0649c20775ed6b78140627","tid":2223860,"uid":18995,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 細路仔信錯超級女權大左膠 何式凝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2295995100627188/posts/%E8%AE%9A%E8%B3%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91-%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E8%A9%B1%E9%